descriptionHtml:
Greybeards-101

This Mod Makes The Greybeard Robes Playable.
You Can Craft The Robes At A Tanning Rack Under The Misc Section.
The Greybeard Outfit Comes With It\'s Own Enchantments:

It Gives The Hood A Health Increase Enchantment Of 70.
It Gives The Robes A Reduce Shout Cooldown Enchantment Of 20%.
It Gives The Boots A Carriage Capacity Increase Enchantment Of 50.

But That Is Not All.
The Greybeards Are Also Killable Now.
If You Want To Be Evil And End The Greybeards Existence U Can Do That Now.

How To Install: Put The File In The Skyrim Data Folder.
author: JP0005
